{"tid":1115890,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人覺得許志安心情應該同鄭中基首無賴一樣？","createTime":"2019-04-19T13:42:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-19T14:02:40.000Z","uid":67294,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cdb3e5cc166c3e39ab28d10c7734427ec559a9ce","tid":1115890,"uid":67294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T13:42:29.000Z","msg":"睇許志安記者會佢只係不斷重覆話自己衰 對唔住Sammi<br />\n<br />\n但佢無講過希望Sammi原諒佢<br />\n<br />\n其實佢兩個拍左咁耐，但無乜見過佢地兩個曬恩愛<br />\nSammi都講過唔知安仔會唔會娶佢又唔敢諗<br />\n<br />\n所以其實安仔咁多年黎只係唔想辜負sammi，可能今次出軌佢自己都覺得唔抵原諒，想放棄呢段情<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n許志安心情應該同鄭中基首無賴一樣<br />\n<br />\n//<br />\n愛我這廢人 出錯你都肯去忍 然而誰亦早知<br />\n不會合襯 偏偏你願意等 為何還喜歡我<br />\n//"},{"pid":"8b8d3cc6fa327526367b247fd263fc3ed28f5772","tid":1115890,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T13:46:05.000Z","msg":"牙安自己大把歌啦"},{"pid":"bcf701de25c4fedb35101fffb24bddc30880e0a4","tid":1115890,"uid":114728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T13:46:38.000Z","msg":"無"},{"pid":"a7569470938c5fe5edc6b751876a0185e28f977f","tid":1115890,"uid":116214,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T14:02:40.000Z","msg":"叫佢聽返自己呢首就差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/F8uCvKHkG9A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FF8uCvKHkG9A&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSVgnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=1a69d853\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/F8uCvKHkG9A</a>"}]}